{"title":"泸沽湖","authors":["晓雪"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":5,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"泸沽湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明的空气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点灰尘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天，白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翡翠般的湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明洁，纯净，晶莹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片迷人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比深沉的宁静。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几叶独木舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在水晶玻璃般的湖面上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在梦幻般醉人的歌声里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠地飘行，飘行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛时间突然站住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几千个春天的翠绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几百代人们的梦境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数美妙的神话传说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都浓缩和消溶在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这深深的湖里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么想永远留下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺在“母海”㈠的怀抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着狮格干姆㈡——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这崇高娴静的女神；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许正是她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住了喧嚣与嘈杂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住了拥挤、混乱和污秽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使这神奇美丽的泸沽湖里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛满了人类最古老而又"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻、纯洁的爱情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"㈠泸沽湖又称母海、女神之海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"㈡狮格干姆是泸沽湖边一座山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的名字，意为掌管狮子的女神。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}